title: Research Assistant Interview
Application Type: I applied in-person. The process took 1 day. I interviewed at JobOne (Calgary, AB) in Apr 2018
Interview Descriptions: Excellent interview and very interesting. The interview experience was great all the people were very friendly. The response was prompt and professional. I would recommend those who apply consider an employers interview ability - the sign of a good company is being able to interview properly.
Interview Questions: What excites you about this company?
